snippet.description:
Amber Rose's Sons Sebastian Taylor and Slash Electric (Video) - 2021

How many kids does Amber Rose have?
The 37-year-old model has two children with two separate baby daddies.

Rose has an eight-year-old son, Sebastian Taylor Thomaz, with rapper Wiz Khalifa.

Her second baby boy, Slash Electric Alexander Edwards, is from her relationship with rapper Alexander Edwards.
